	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes, it's true.  The problem with fixing the RAM, is that you have to do it without ever removing the power.  The only way I know of to fix one is by using a CopyNES.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


