		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />As far as I know, no dump of the ROM exists.  So unless some enterprising fellow with a CopyNES decides to do it, I will be eventually screwed.  At least $100 gone to waste.  Of course, I could keep stacking batteries to delay the evil day.

		

